features: 3 Pcs Frisbee Dog Toy Set with Vibrant Colors: Includes 1 red, 1 orange, and 1 blue frisbee for dogs, perfect for outdoor play and training. These dog frisbees are designed to withstand aggressive chewers while keeping your pup entertained and mentally stimulated. Ideal for fetch, obedience drills, or backyard fun.

Durable and Safe Frisbee Dog Toy Crafted for Tough Play: Made of high quality material, this frisbee for dogs resists cracks and tears. Its flexible yet rugged design ensures long-lasting use, making it a top choice for outdoor dog toys that survive high-energy sessions.

Optimized Size for All Breeds: Dog Training Frisbee: Each frisbee dog toy measures 18.8cm in diameter and 0.7cm thick, offering a lightweight, easy-to-catch shape. Great for puppy training toys or adult dog exercise, its ergonomic edge supports smooth throws and gentle jaw impact.

Perfect for Active Dogs and Training Enthusiasts: Whether teaching agility, burning energy, or bonding outdoors, these frisbee dog toys suit pet owners, trainers, and playful pups. Use them in parks, beaches, or backyards for interactive play that reduces boredom and anxiety.

Upgrade Playtime with Dog Frisbee Toys: Combine fun and function! This 3-pack frisbee for dogs doubles as chew-resistant puppy training toys and durable outdoor dog toys. Bright colors enhance visibility, while the tough build ensures endless fetch sessions without wear.
